&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2O
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
 RUN_TYPE     GEO_OPT
&END

&GEOOPT
 OPTIMIZER CG
 MAX_ITER  2
 USE_FIT_LINE_SEARCH
 MAX_STEEP_STEPS 1
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       100
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 EPS_SCF  0.00001
&END

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q1
&END

&KIND O
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q6
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          4.0 4.0 4.0
&END

&COORD
 H   0.0 0.0 0.0
 H   0.9 0.0 0.0
&END
